      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Grid-convergence index (GCI) below 5% for hemolysis index QoI.",
      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study (2.1 M, 6.8 M, 18.4 M cells) yields GCI of 3.2% for normalized hemolysis index; Richardson extrapolation confirms asymptotic range."
    },
